summary: My favourite Ningheim racemenu preset shared with the world.
descriptionHtml:
This is a fairly simple character preset which I use with my female Ningheim character.

Required mods:

- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]Racemenu[/url]
- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35474]The Ningheim race[/url]﻿
- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411]Brows[/url] (Ningheim add-on)

Recommended mods (used in the screenshots)

- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]
- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72617]SKY Female Textures[/url] (Ningheim UNP)
- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62639]Empyrean Warpaints - Custom Series (female)[/url]﻿
- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363]KS Hairdos - HDT Physics[/url]﻿
- [url=https://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73848]Tetrachromatic ENB[/url]﻿

Enjoy!
author: DaedricKitty
